data.meta_description: Jeanne is the daughter of Nicolas Prévost and Claude Masson. She was baptized on the above date. She married Gaston Guay before 1654, in Montreuil, France. They are the parents of the following (verified with PRDH): 1) Mathieu (1654-1719) md Marie-Therese Poirier dit Bellepoire 2) Marguerite (abt 1661-1702) md Noel...
